headline: Phillips 66 (NYSE:PSX) Reports 67% Shareholder Return And US$14 Billion Return To Investors
summary: Phillips 66 (NYSE:PSX) saw its stock price rise by 9% over the last week, likely buoyed by the company's recent investor presentation that underscored strong past performance with total shareholder returns of 67% since CEO Mark Lashier's leadership began in 2022. While the broader market was up 7% over the same period, Phillips 66's proactive communication with stakeholders, strategic asset management, and significant capital return initiatives of over $14 billion might have provided...

headline: Elliott Management Releases Investor Presentation on Phillips 66
summary: Elliott Investment Management L.P. ("Elliott"), which manages funds that together make it a top-five shareholder in Phillips 66 (NYSE: PSX) (the "Company" or "Phillips"), today released an investor presentation titled "Streamline 66: Elliott's Perspectives on Value Creation."
